<plot>Winston Thorpe (Morin) suspects his wife, Indigo, (Branch) of having an affair. The obsessive millionaire hires a slimy Scottish private-eye, Angus Stewart, (Andrews) to tail his wife and get the proof he needs to take action. But Angus and Indigo form a romantic alliance right after she agrees to steal her husband's Imperial Egg and give Angus half its worth. Angus agrees to help the oppressed Indigo "disappear", but the new lovers get careless and Winston starts finding evidence that link the two together. He soon finds the proof he needs to take deadly action of his own.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?110504</url></doc>
